KitKat::

She looked back inward down the hall and sighed. "Even a good leader 
can make a bad dicision every once in a while. Perhaps I have done 
the same here. But I will not give up so easily."  She turned and in 
wolf mode, went running in a dead run out into the forest. 

She needed to burn off some off the extra energy, plus run off the 
anger she had for Maxima. She wondered why this bot whom did show 
promise was given so much favor, while showing little in the ways of 
leadership. She kept running and running, dodging trees and jumping 
over logs.  She stopped at a stream and layed down. Her stomach was 
creating great pain for her.  She was about to turn and go back, when 
she caught a strange scent on the wind.  She got up and started 
walking to the scent.
